<item>
            <title>[LU-1443] Update Test Scripts to Replace all Bugzilla Bug References with LU Jira Tickets</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1443</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should no longer be referencing bugzilla bugs as reasons for disabling tests. Each bz bug cited as a reason for disabling a test should be copied over to an LU ticket in Jira and the test script updated to reference the new LU ticket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following are some of the references I&apos;ve noticed while reviewing our tests:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obdfilter_survey - test_1b - bz23791, test_2b - bz23791&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-sec - test_2 - bz19430, test_5 - bz19967, test_6 - bz19967&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-vbr - test_11a - bz23385, test_12a - bz16356&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-dual - test_15c - bz10124&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;recovery-small - test_24 - bz5494, test_52 - bz5493&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity - test_27u - bz13297, test_42a - bz2108, test_42b - bz9789, test_42c - bz3637, test_42d - bz9789, test_45 - bz3561, test_68b - bz5188&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanityn - test_14b - bz3192, test_19 bz15528/3811, test_22 - bz16929, test_28 - bz9977, test_29 - bz15528/11549, test_35 - bz18080&lt;/p&gt;</description>
